//Relation introduction
   (A --> C), (B --> D), neq(A,B), neq(C,D) |- ((A,B) --> (C,D)), (Belief:Intersection)
   (A --> C), (A --> D), neq(C,D)           |- ((A,A) --> {C,D}), (Belief:Intersection)
   (C --> A), (D --> A), neq(C,D)           |- ({C,D} --> (A,A)), (Belief:Intersection)

